  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个基础设施组件的依赖流程图。核心是从Redis缓存开始，用户注册后会先落到Redis，然后有两个分支走向。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Infra_RedisCache"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，所以起点是RedisCache。那两个分支分别指向哪里？是并行处理还是有先后顺序？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Infra_RedisCache"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "一条分支去Etcd集群做验证，另一条直接去IngressController做确认。验证通过之后，Etcd会再流转到WorkerNode进行审批。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Infra_EtcdCluster",
        "Infra_IngressController",
        "Infra_WorkerNode"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "好的，我梳理一下：RedisCache同时连EtcdCluster和IngressController，然后EtcdCluster再指向WorkerNode。IngressController那边还有后续吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Infra_RedisCache",
        "Infra_EtcdCluster",
        "Infra_IngressController",
        "Infra_WorkerNode"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "IngressController确认完成后，需要回连到EtcdCluster那边，形成一个闭环校验。这样整个流程才能完整。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Infra_IngressController",
        "Infra_EtcdCluster"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "画好了，RedisCache作为起点，分出两条线：一条到EtcdCluster，一条到IngressController。EtcdCluster再到WorkerNode，同时IngressController回指EtcdCluster。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Infra_RedisCache",
        "Infra_EtcdCluster",
        "Infra_IngressController",
        "Infra_WorkerNode"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "等等，IngressController回指的方向好像反了？应该是IngressController指向EtcdCluster，不是反过来。另外节点标签需要调整——实际用的是pendingApproval、pendingConfirmation这些状态名，不是直接写组件名。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Infra_IngressController",
        "Infra_EtcdCluster",
        "pendingApproval",
        "pendingConfirmation"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "收到，我修正一下：pendingConfirmation节点从IngressController过来，然后指向thanksVerifying。pendingApproval对应WorkerNode。所有连线方向再核对一遍。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "pendingConfirmation",
        "Infra_IngressController",
        "thanksVerifying",
        "pendingApproval",
        "Infra_WorkerNode"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对的，现在结构正确了。thanksSigningUp作为RedisCache的入口，两条分支分别到thanksVerifying和pendingConfirmation，再加上pendingApproval的收尾，完整了。",
